-- Flaherty Says He’s Comfortable With Canada’s Housing Market
-- B y   T h e o p h i l o s   A r g i t i s
-- 2013-09-17T20:21:57Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-09-17/flaherty-says-he-s-comfortable-with-canada-s-housing-market.html
Canadian Finance Minister  Jim
Flaherty  said he’s “comfortable” with the nation’s housing
market after it slowed.  Flaherty, speaking in an interview with BNN TV, said a
“calming” in the market has been a positive development.  To contact the reporter on this story:
